	   <tr><td colspan=2>when i needed money bad i just went to the zones where the higher level people where hunting and vendors where not around.&nbsp;&nbsp;in such a case most high levels don't want to mess with lugging around all the fine steel mobs drop.  so i take it off their hands for them.  i stayed invisible while their parties fought and i picked up the table scraps.  couple hours of that and i was a couple hundred plat richer.  and magicians can carry more fine steel loot then anyone else around because we can summon those dimensional containers that have 100% weight reduction.  very usefull now that they don't poof when you get disconnected unless you don't log on within 30 minutes.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
